{"tid":1730013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不要開花，去反包圍","createTime":"2019-11-17T12:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:12:06.000Z","uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d51d53a4b4b7024e0f7cd452e8af0e896b01cc7d","tid":1730013,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"不要開花，去反包圍。人生沒有那麼多時間給你去圍魏救趙 ，出來就去反包。擋路有什麼用還是會被冇視。圍不到就火魔，Tg就散開再聚。大不了扑狗，你連手腳都不敢打斷還好意思說救手足。倒地之後繼續獅鳥，打撚到讓牠開始懷疑自己的犬生，讓牠覺得牠的意義就是被你打柒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wthtECA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwthtECA.jpg&h=ba4fb19d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f24ac111c41466fc59ab8e2daf2ee872036c66d","tid":1730013,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2199c326c9d585d111accdf9611ab624f56cd3c","tid":1730013,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f51828b57d23d1ed534a5fb4cbc364758eb89fc","tid":1730013,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"推 要打個缺口救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1098795a0d33879f528fa63e12a3901a481374a","tid":1730013,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eeb34edc84691331a6c1019dc9e8b07bf87f816","tid":1730013,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"旺角嗰班自己比狗圍埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk